# metadataObjectsCallbackQueue

**Instance Property**

The dispatch queue on which to execute the delegate’s methods.

## Declaration

```swift
var metadataObjectsCallbackQueue: dispatch_queue_t? { get }
```

## Discussion

To set the dispatch queue, you must use the [doc://com.apple.avfoundation/documentation/AVFoundation/AVCaptureMetadataOutput/setMetadataObjectsDelegate(_:queue:)] method.

## Receiving captured metadata objects

- **setMetadataObjectsDelegate(_:queue:)**: Sets the delegate and dispatch queue to use handle callbacks.
- **metadataObjectsDelegate**: The delegate of the capture metadata output object.
- **AVCaptureMetadataOutputObjectsDelegate**: Methods for receiving metadata produced by a metadata capture output.
